---
title: Cal Smart Pork Patties in Tikka Sauce with Cilantro Rice
description: Flecks of cilantro stems don't just make these pork patties look pretty—they also add a ton of flavour! Tikka sauce blends beautifully with cream cheese to give this curry a velvety texture without the heaviness.
